OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779879767
OL,3,CRacecourse hosts historic event to
OL,4,Ccelebrate 170 years of racing
OL,6,FThe event recognises the first
OL,7,Frecorded modern race meeting held at
OL,8,FCartmel on Whit Monday in 1856, and
OL,9,Faims to recreate the spirit of those
OL,10,Fearly gatherings when race days were
OL,11,Fas much a rural festival as a sporting
OL,12,Foccasion.
OL,14,FVisitors can expect a full afternoon
OL,15,Fof jump racing, alongside a lively
OL,16,Fprogramme of traditional country
OL,17,Fsports and entertainment designed to
OL,18,Freflect the historic character of the
OL,19,Fmeeting.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
