PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779879767
OL,3,CRacecourse hosts historic event to
OL,4,Ccelebrate 170 years of racing
OL,6,FCartmel Racecourse Director Geraldine
OL,7,FMcKay, said: "When racing first took
OL,8,Fplace at Cartmel in the nineteenth
OL,9,Fcentury it was a true community
OL,10,Fgathering, bringing together sport,
OL,11,Fspectacle and celebration.
OL,13,F"The Cartmel Gathering is our way of
OL,14,Fhonouring that heritage by recreating
OL,15,Fsomething of the atmosphere those
OL,16,Fearly visitors would have experienced.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
