FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779879767
OL,3,CRacecourse hosts historic event to
OL,4,Ccelebrate 170 years of racing
OL,6,F"Cartmel has always been about more
OL,7,Fthan racing - it's about people coming
OL,8,Ftogether, enjoying great sport and
OL,9,Fcelebrating the character of our local
OL,10,Fcommunity."
OL,12,FTo mark the occasion, a Cumberland and
OL,13,FWestmorland wrestling competition, one
OL,14,Fof the county's oldest sporting
OL,15,Ftraditions, will be held, bringing
OL,16,Ftogether some of the region's top
OL,17,Fwrestlers to compete at the racecourse.
OL,26,@rD@KO]
