CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779879767
OL,3,CRacecourse hosts historic event to
OL,4,Ccelebrate 170 years of racing
OL,6,FHoward Tindall of the Cumberland &
OL,7,FWestmorland Wrestling Association
OL,8,Fsaid: "Cumberland and Westmorland
OL,9,Fwrestling has been part of gatherings
OL,10,Fand rural celebrations across Cumbria
OL,11,Ffor generations. It's wonderful to see
OL,12,FCartmel embracing that heritage and
OL,13,Fstaging a fully accredited competition
OL,14,Fas part of the celebrations. The
OL,15,Fcostume competition will also showcase
OL,16,Fone of the most colourful and
OL,17,Fdistinctive traditions in British
OL,18,Fsport."
OL,26,@pD@GOUzD@GO]
