OL,3,CRacecourse hosts historic event to
OL,4,Ccelebrate 170 years of racing
OL,6,FThe programme will also include a
OL,7,Ftraditional wrestling costume
OL,8,Fcompetition to celebrate the distinct
OL,9,Fattire of the sport, including velvet
OL,10,Fwrestling trunks traditionally worn by
OL,11,Fcompetitors and creatively embroidered.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
